text: Yury Shakhmuradov (born 27 February 1942) is a Soviet wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 78 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the Soviet Union Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Jabrayil District
title: Yury Shakhmuradov
